{"data":[{"author":"Kunalpod","capabilities":[],"category_id":"5261a8fb3b773043d500000f","category_name":"Tools & Utilities","category_color":"fdbf37","changelog":[{"version":"1.0","published_date":"2015-07-26T10:25:22.317Z","release_notes":""}],"companions":{"ios":null,"android":{"id":"55b4b572138347521f00003e","icon":"https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/KfJ1ZQKXR36QiuOr1SG6","name":"Plip","url":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.podkunal.hackindia_plip","required":true,"pebblekit_version":"3"}},"compatibility":{"ios":{"supported":false},"android":{"supported":true},"aplite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":2}},"basalt":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"chalk":{"supported":false,"firmware":{"major":3}},"diorite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}},"emery":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":3}}},"created_at":"2015-07-19T15:08:25.994Z","description":"Location sharing. Secure. Simple.\r\n\r\nThis watchapp looks very much like an ordinary watchface, but really isn't. It detects (right-side) button presses in the following order\r\n\"UP-CENTER-DOWN\"\r\nand the moment you do press it in said manner your phone sends your location to all the contacts you have chosen on the supporting application, via text message(SMS).\r\n\r\nThis app hence aims to be a sort of discrete SOS/ location sharing app, that could either be used to track children/old people or used in general emergency situations. \r\n\r\nThis concept and design also happens to be the winner of HackIndia-2015 under the category - Use of Pebble smartwatch to create a useful and intuitive  application.\r\n\r\n\r\nPlease do provide any feedback on improvements.","developer_id":"54d0dbb3dec337644f000099","header_images":[{"orig":"https://assets.getpebble.com/api/file/ztYov9R4SWjv6oUg1KQt/convert?cache=true&fit=crop","720x320":"https://assets.getpebble.com/api/file/ztYov9R4SWjv6oUg1KQt/convert?cache=true&fit=crop&w=720&h=320"}],"hearts":4,"icon_image":{"28x28":"https://assets.get